   United States Postal Service: Postcard Concerning Suspicious Letters or
   Parcels
   Also available in: Spanish
   Every household in America, every rental Post Office box and all
   military APO and FPO addresses will receive this post card. It contains
   information on what to look for if you suspect a letter or package may
   contain a harmful biological agent.
